rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I might just be imagining things...
but I could have sworn I heard odd
noises out on the Lud Cloudway.

rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0002
rows.name:
They say the sounds are just a
monster's call, but I'm not so sure
myself.

rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, it's not like anyone's heard
these kinds of sounds before!

rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It's getting to the point where I
can't sleep for thinking about it.

rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Really? You'll set up watch
and investigate for me?

rows.label: tlk47400164_04_msg0007
rows.name:
The noise goes right through you, so
you might need to grit your teeth.
